data.description: Great country home with just under 6 acres and close to Deer River. Main level has 3 bedrooms, a full bath and a large kitchen with patio doors off the dining area to the deck. Appliance package included. The lower level features walk out basement with large family room, 4th bedroom, ¾ bath, laundry room and office. Insulated and heated 25x46 garage. Nice back yard with a large playground set that will remain. Circle drive, and compliant septic.
